Subject: [PATCH] Drop tracing-level log statements that depend on kv-log-macro

---
 src/task/builder.rs | 40 ++++++++++++++++++++--------------------
 1 file changed, 20 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/task/builder.rs b/src/task/builder.rs
